      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/25/50",
      "text": [
        ": \"إِذَا اُغْتُصِبَتْ أَمَةٌ فَاقْتُضَّتْ فَعَلَيْهِ عُشْرُ ثَمَنِهَا فَإِذَا كَانَتْ حُرَّةً فَعَلَيْهِ اَلصَّدَاقُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4465 - Talhah ibn Zayd narrated from Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) from his father, Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) that Ali (as) said:\n\"If a bondwoman is raped and her virginity is taken, the perpetrator must pay one-tenth of her value. However, if she is a free woman, he must pay the dowry.\""
        ]
      }
